snippet.title: MarbleScience
snippet.description:
Hey, it's Tobias from MarbleScience.

I make science videos and my goal is to use the illustrative power of simple simulation models to convey meaningful knowledge about various topics. 

Making a MarbleScience video is a tremendous amount of work. It is something I genuinely enjoy, but it is clearly more then I could bear doing in evenings after work or on weekends. Now, I am not naive enough to believe that I just need to ask nicely and all my expenses are covered, but already a sign that, with a reasonable growth of the community, the channel might one day sustain itself would be a great help to ensure the future of MarbleScience.

Thank you so much for considering to support MarbleScience! Your subscription means a lot to me and if you want to help even more, you can find further information on my Patreon page. Thank you. I greatly appreciate it!

Warm Regards,
Tobias
